<item>
            <title>[LU-15046] osp precreate thread can get stuck</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15046</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;osp precreate thread can race with osp_obd_connect() which initializes lcs_exp (required for fid client). then if the precreate thread finds lcs_exp uninitialized it can get stuck blocking all precreating logic.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
